{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":227175,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Piotr Łazarkiewicz","original_name":"Piotr Łazarkiewicz","popularity":0.0957,"profile_path":"/mI7GivwbtEem7xSMFgdyHJQZxxr.jpg","known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/fBE8jN0CuG3TgX4kgpDcXtZwemb.jpg","id":42983,"title":"A Woman Alone","original_title":"Kobieta samotna","overview":"Irena, a postal delivery worker, is struggling with inadequate housing, a drunk neighbor who wants to take her place, and a heartless boss, knowing that the whole day at work, she is leaving her young son. But the worst is the loneliness, exacerbated by her single mother status. She meets a crippled pensioner Jacek, who appears to be the key to her happiness, but tragedy continues to strike.","poster_path":"/95oSXqkPQZOX9MxteoYpxRt17t8.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"pl","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2476,"release_date":"1987-03-15","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.6,"vote_count":13},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/NRkDQYifIh4S0Ib2ie7NFmV2vy.jpg","id":581841,"title":"A Time for Witches","original_title":"Pora na czarownice","overview":"Twenty years old prostitute and drug addict, Jola, by chance meets Andrzej, a \"railway station gay\". They try to stay together, in spite of numerous diffculties. They both are carriers of the HIV virus. At the end of their travels they find themselves in the Red Palace - formerly the recreation centre for Party dignitaries, now a home for AIDS sufferers - which is run by father Jan. In the nearby small town aggression begins to grow again the unwanted guests; the house have been promised to the local people for housing purposes... The lives and fates of Jola, Andrzej, and father Jan become increasingly intertwined with one another...","poster_path":"/tDjq0KsF0CoDoNeR2vrZIuZk6U4.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"pl","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4425,"release_date":"1994-02-28","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":4.8,"vote_count":4},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":62299,"title":"Zero_jeden_zero","original_title":"Zero_jeden_zero","overview":"It promises to be quite an ordinary day. A day during which viewers have the opportunity to peep into the lives of seven couples. It may seem that the camera captures snatches of the lives of random characters. This is an illusion. These people, although they do not know each other, once witnessed a certain accident that left its mark on them. On each different, but still... The first couple: Maciek and Lena. He was involved in a car accident. He was traveling with his lover at the time. Now he is confined to a wheelchair. He suspects his wife of infidelity. His obsession, harassment and aggression ruin their lives. Couple two: Kasia has found the man she wants to spend her life with. When the boyfriend confesses to her that until recently he was a woman, she can't explain it to herself. Couples three, four, five, six and seven also have their own dramas, secrets.","poster_path":"/2KrQfd6jPbyQQ89bbZwrl8g3p9k.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"pl","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1183,"release_date":"2008-11-14","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":2.0,"vote_count":3}]}],"total_pages":1,"total_results":1}